-- Janus bond chief Smith says was consulted on Bill Gross hire
-- By Ross Kerber
-- Tue Oct 07, 2014 02:23PM EDT
-- None



BOSTON, Oct 7 (Reuters) - Janus Capital Group Inc<JNS.N> bond chief Gibson Smith said he was consulted by Janus CEO Richard Weil before the Denver asset manager hired star bond fund manager Bill Gross from Pimco.

